name: Feizy Contour Rug in Rust-3'-6" x 5'-6"
meta_title: Feizy Contour Rug in Rust-3'-6" x 5'-6"
description: An intricate display of moving lines in brilliant colors: the Contour Collection. Strokes of rust, mocha and cinnamon swirl across the silky pile, sparking images as diverse as rustic sunsets, nomadic tapestries or even modern art. Versatile and striking, this collection will infuse imagination into your home.
construction: Hand tufted in India with an antique washed, semi-worsted and twisted New Zealand wool and art silk pile.

name: Feizy Channels Rug in Ivory-4' x 6'
meta_title: Feizy Channels Rug in Ivory-4' x 6'
description: The calm, quiet splendor of the Channels Collection defies the boundaries of elegance and style. Flowing geometric patterns integrated with natural soothing tones create a balanced ebb and flow to both modern and transitional décors. The sensuous patina of deep lush piles plays against shorter looped piles to capture visual interest with contrasting textures.
construction: Tibetan-style hand knotted in India with a pure wool pile.

Resplendent blossoms and wings of wheat float across the soft pile in warm flaxen, fiery and forest tones. Designs of cascading leaves will perfectly adorn your home regardless of the season.
construction: Hand knotted in India with a premium Seridian wool pile.

name: Feizy Qing Rug in Camel-4' x 6'
meta_title: Feizy Qing Rug in Camel-4' x 6'
description: In Chinese, the word “qing” means clarity or purity, or a blue or green that can span the spectrum from the clearest sky to the blackest sea. Feizy's® Qing Collection is a grouping of designs that are Asian-inspired collages. Patchwork designs, florals and screen patterns are lovingly hand knotted in a pile of wool with art silk accents to add shimmering details to each pattern.
construction: Tibetan-style hand knotted in India with an antique washed, Seridian wool and art silk pile.

Patchwork designs, florals and screen patterns are lovingly hand knotted in a pile of wool with art silk accents to add shimmering details to each pattern.
construction: Tibetan-style hand knotted in India with an antique washed, Seridian wool and art silk pile.

Literally translated, “dim sum” means “touch the heart.” Elegantly simple yet incredibly striking, these unique pieces will become the heart of any setting in which they are placed.

name: Feizy Saphir Rug in Ivory / Silver-2'-2" x 4'
meta_title: Feizy Saphir Rug in Ivory / Silver-2'-2" x 4'
description: The trendsetting Saphir Collection is a grouping of impressive designs machine woven in a mixture of high and low textures to give each piece an interesting textural appeal. The art silk designs are so dense and lush, they seem to dance across the flat woven fields, and they are easily mistaken for handmade masterpieces. Soft and flexible, each piece is woven in a variety of warm and vibrant colors to re-interpret traditional designs and update transitional patterns.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a multi-textured art silk pile.

Soft and flexible, each piece is woven in a variety of warm and vibrant colors to re-interpret traditional designs and update transitional patterns.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a multi-textured art silk pile.

name: Feizy Goshen Rug in Gold/Brown-3'-6" x 5'-6"
meta_title: Feizy Goshen Rug in Gold/Brown-3'-6" x 5'-6"
description: Old World sensibilities and a contemporary color palette unite in the Goshen Collection of hand woven Soumaks. Inspired by the classics, time-honored patterns have been recreated in exquisite detail in muted tones of gold, red, brown and black with rich accents of terra cotta, sage and cream.  Utterly adaptable, each piece is reversible one side showcasing the chain stitch weave, the other a smooth traditional loop to create a wealth of decorating possibilities.
construction: Soumak hand woven in India with an antique washed, premium pure wool pile.

description: The designs of the Ustad Collection are a return to the classics, featuring time-honored designs hand knotted in updated palettes to coordinate with today's décor trends. The well-balanced mix of tradition and innovation in the pattern of each rug transcends the common to capture the beauty of a vanished world. Trending toward the tribal, the pure wool pile of each piece creates a harmonious blend of modern style and classic design. Warm colors and a dazzling sheen add to the allure of this collection.
construction: Hand knotted in India with an antique washed, hand-spun, premium pure wool pile.

name: Feizy Saphir Cabo Rug in Cream / Aqua-2'-2" x 4'
meta_title: Feizy Saphir Cabo Rug in Cream / Aqua-2'-2" x 4'
description: Rich browns, soft ivories and calming aquas and teals are the hallmarks of the Saphir Cabo Collection.  Transitional and contemporary patterns are power loomed in Feizy's acclaimed Saphir construction.  Often imitated but never duplicated, the high-low piles are woven in plush art silk.  Playful patterns and on-trend colors impart casual charm to any setting.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a multi-textured art silk pile.

description: A cool palette and unforgettable transitional and traditional designs are the hallmarks of the Starnes Collection.  Power loomed in a polypropylene pile, each piece features blues ranging from midnight to sky as well as a host of other soothing spa tones like beiges, browns and ivories.  Revitalize a room's décor by making a dramatic statement with any rug from this stunning group.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a polypropylene fiber pile.

Each bold design is versatile enough to enhance an understated decorating theme or add that extra touch of pizzazz to more elaborate settings. The Lucka Collection is machine woven in 100% polypropylene and is fade-resistant. A quick spray with the garden hose cleans away heavy soil.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey in a polypropylene fiber pile.

description: The Azeri Collections feature soft contemporary and transitional designs power loomed in a plush pile of wool with art silk highlights.  Ikat, erased traditional and intricate iron-work designs are woven in a variety of palettes that feature hues of gray ranging from silver to charcoal, chocolate and ecru.  Superior softness and striking highlights are the hallmarks of these designs.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a wool and art silk pile.

description: The Saphir Rubus Collection features transitional and contemporary designs power loomed in saturated raspberry tones and cool hues of gray.  Woven in Feizy's best-selling Saphir construction, the incredibly soft, high-low designs are at once striking and comfortable and suited for settings that range from the super casual to the super chic.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a multi-textured art silk pile.

meta_title: Feizy Azeri Ii Rug in Dark Chocolate / Ecru-2'-2" x 4'
description: The Azeri Collections feature soft contemporary and transitional designs power loomed in a plush pile of wool with art silk highlights.  Ikat, erased traditional and intricate iron-work designs are woven in a variety of palettes that feature hues of gray ranging from silver to charcoal, chocolate and ecru.  Superior softness and striking highlights are the hallmarks of these designs.

Transitional and contemporary patterns range from erased ikats to kaleidoscope images to large-scale stylized florals.  Each design is masterfully power loomed in a palette of grays, taupes and black, and is intricately shaded to impart movement.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a polypropylene fiber pile.

description: The Lorrain Collection utilizes a technique similar to tie-dying.   Monochromatic tones are represented in bold patterns and in hues of varying saturation to create a watercolor effect.  These breezy pieces are hand hooked and suited to a variety of casual living spaces.
construction: Hand hooked in India with a pure wool pile.

name: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua-4' x 6'
meta_title: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua-4' x 6'
description: The designers of Tracy Porter's Poetic Wanderlust and Feizy Rugs have created the ultimate in casual elegance The Rumi Collection.  Each hand knotted piece is created using a palette of vibrant yarns, which are shorn closely to expose the warp and weft of the rug.  These bold designs are then washed to give the distressed,  vintage look of an heirloom that has been handed down for generations.Please note: Because of the rug's construction and its closely-shorn pile, you will be able to see the warp and weft fibers.  Where weft fibers are tied on to one another, you will notice a slight irregularity in the foundation of the rug.  Please note that this is simply a characteristic of the type of rug, and it is not considered a defect.
construction: Hand knotted in India in an antique washed and closely shorn wool pile.

meta_title: Feizy Rumi Rug in Graphite-2' x 3'
description: The designers of Tracy Porter's Poetic Wanderlust and Feizy Rugs have created the ultimate in casual elegance The Rumi Collection.  Each hand knotted piece is created using a palette of vibrant yarns, which are shorn closely to expose the warp and weft of the rug.  These bold designs are then washed to give the distressed,  vintage look of an heirloom that has been handed down for generations.Please note: Because of the rug's construction and its closely-shorn pile, you will be able to see the warp and weft fibers.  Where weft fibers are tied on to one another, you will notice a slight irregularity in the foundation of the rug.  Please note that this is simply a characteristic of the type of rug, and it is not considered a defect.
construction: Hand knotted in India in an antique washed and closely shorn wool pile.

name: Feizy Burke Rug in Atlantic-4' x 6'
meta_title: Feizy Burke Rug in Atlantic-4' x 6'
description: The Burke Collection's unique look comes from a technique that combines hand looming and hand knotting.  The result is a collection that has a distressed look but still feels luxurious.  Color varies in intensity throughout the hand spun viscose yarns and the subtle sheen plays beautifully against the more rustic wool fibers.  Thin, flexible and incredibly versatile, these pieces work well in a variety of settings.
construction: Hand loomed and knotted in India in wool and art silk.

description: The Burke Collection's unique look comes from a technique that combines hand looming and hand knotting.  The result is a collection that has a distressed look but still feels luxurious.  Color varies in intensity throughout the hand spun viscose yarns and the subtle sheen plays beautifully against the more rustic wool fibers.  Thin, flexible and incredibly versatile, these pieces work well in a variety of settings.
construction: Hand loomed and knotted in India in wool and art silk.

description: The Thatcher Collection is a grouping of power loomed rugs woven in a zero-pile construction to lend it a distressed look.  Reminiscent of many antique pieces, muted hues are accented with bright pops of primary colors.  These traditional and transitional designs breathe new life into a room with on-trend colors and timeless patterns.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a polypropylene fiber pile.

name: Feizy Gramercy Rug in Fog-4' x 6'

description: Soothing neutrals, blues and violets and a plush pile soften the geometric patterns of the Gramercy Collection.  Hand loomed of art silk, each piece features beautiful variation of tones within each design.  The hand carving imparts movement and textural interest.
construction: Hand loomed in India in an art silk pile.

description: Feizy's Abbey Collection combines the beauty of a pastel palette with the soft hand and shimmering pile of viscose.  The result is a grouping of quiet elegance.  Power loomed in cool tones of celadon, ivory and sky, each transitional design lends an air of tranquility to its surroundings.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with an art silk pile.

With a machine-made, comfortably dense construction of bright, coastal color combinations of teal, grey and coral, this collection is the perfect summery look for today.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a polypropylene fiber pile.

name: Feizy Cosmo Rug in Dusk-3'-6" x 5'-6"
meta_title: Feizy Cosmo Rug in Dusk-3'-6" x 5'-6"
description: The Cosmo Collection is a hand tufted bamboo viscose rug hiding a surprise...a jacquard rug on the back!  With completely different, beautifully modern designs on each side in complementary colors, these pieces are versatile, durable and offer the ability to change the look and feel of a room with a simple flip of the rug.
construction: Hand tufted and jacquard backed in India in a bamboo viscose pile.

name: Feizy Contour Rug in Rust
meta_title: Feizy Contour Rug in Rust
description: An intricate display of moving lines in brilliant colors: the Contour Collection. description: The Indochine Collection is a wonderfully plush and luxurious shag that has been table tufted of art silk and simulates the feel of animal fur. The sheen that these rugs possess makes them a playful addition to more casual, contemporary settings.
construction: Table tufted in China with an art silk shag pile.

name: Feizy Qing Rug in Camel
meta_title: Feizy Qing Rug in Camel
description: In Chinese, the word “qing” means clarity or purity, or a blue or green that can span the spectrum from the clearest sky to the blackest sea. Feizy's® Qing Collection is a grouping of designs that are Asian-inspired collages. Patchwork designs, florals and screen patterns are lovingly hand knotted in a pile of wool with art silk accents to add shimmering details to each pattern.
construction: Tibetan-style hand knotted in India with an antique washed, Seridian wool and art silk pile.

name: Feizy Dim Sum Rug in Black / Zinc
meta_title: Feizy Dim Sum Rug in Black / Zinc
description: Chinese screen patterns come to life in the Dim Sum Collection. Tibetan-style hand knotted in New Zealand wool and art silk, this shimmering collection of designs is offered in a variety of stunning colorways that fit easily into contemporary décor. Literally translated, “dim sum” means “touch the heart.” Elegantly simple yet incredibly striking, these unique pieces will become the heart of any setting in which they are placed.
construction: Tibetan-style hand knotted in India with a multi-textured, semi-worsted New Zealand wool and art silk pile.

name: Feizy Saphir Rug in Ivory / Silver
meta_title: Feizy Saphir Rug in Ivory / Silver
description: The trendsetting Saphir Collection is a grouping of impressive designs machine woven in a mixture of high and low textures to give each piece an interesting textural appeal. The art silk designs are so dense and lush, they seem to dance across the flat woven fields, and they are easily mistaken for handmade masterpieces. Soft and flexible, each piece is woven in a variety of warm and vibrant colors to re-interpret traditional designs and update transitional patterns.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a multi-textured art silk pile.

name: Feizy Goshen Rug in Gold/Brown
meta_title: Feizy Goshen Rug in Gold/Brown
description: Old World sensibilities and a contemporary color palette unite in the Goshen Collection of hand woven Soumaks. Inspired by the classics, time-honored patterns have been recreated in exquisite detail in muted tones of gold, red, brown and black with rich accents of terra cotta, sage and cream.  Utterly adaptable, each piece is reversible one side showcasing the chain stitch weave, the other a smooth traditional loop to create a wealth of decorating possibilities.
construction: Soumak hand woven in India with an antique washed, premium pure wool pile.

name: Feizy Ustad Rug in Camel/Black
meta_title: Feizy Ustad Rug in Camel/Black
description: The designs of the Ustad Collection are a return to the classics, featuring time-honored designs hand knotted in updated palettes to coordinate with today's décor trends. The well-balanced mix of tradition and innovation in the pattern of each rug transcends the common to capture the beauty of a vanished world. Trending toward the tribal, the pure wool pile of each piece creates a harmonious blend of modern style and classic design. Warm colors and a dazzling sheen add to the allure of this collection.
construction: Hand knotted in India with an antique washed, hand-spun, premium pure wool pile.

meta_title: Feizy Amzad Rug in Light Blue
description: Trends toward modern and transitional home furnishings inspired designer Tracy Porter's Poetic Wanderlust™ and Feizy Rugs® designers to create the Amzad Collection. Traditional damask, floral and panel designs are stylized and woven in an updated palette of warm spice tones and cool blues and grays. Hand knotted in premium New Zealand wool, each piece is antique finished to impart movement in the design and background as well as a soft hand.
construction: Hand knotted in India with an antique washed, premium New Zealand wool pile.

description: The Coronado Collection of printed jute rugs features the best-selling whimsical designs of Tracy Porter's Poetic Wanderlust brand.  Bold colors and natural jute combine to create pieces that are casual and on-trend.  Backed in canvas, these rugs have more body than a traditional jute rug and are designed for durability as well as beauty.
construction: Hand loomed in India in a printed, woven jute and backed in canvas.

description: The Azeri Collections feature soft contemporary and transitional designs power loomed in a plush pile of wool with art silk highlights.  Ikat, erased traditional and intricate iron-work designs are woven in a variety of palettes that feature hues of gray ranging from silver to charcoal, chocolate and ecru.  Superior softness and striking highlights are the hallmarks of these designs.
construction: Power loomed in Turkey with a wool and art silk pile.

meta_title: Feizy Harlow Rug in Meadow

Power loomed in a palette of ivory and varying shades of blues and greens, transitional and updated traditional patterns dance across the piles of each piece.  Close attention to detail has yielded dynamic designs with delicate shading usually only found in hand knotted pieces.

Each design is masterfully power loomed in a palette of grays, taupes and black, and is intricately shaded to impart movement.

name: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua
meta_title: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua
description: The designers of Tracy Porter's Poetic Wanderlust and Feizy Rugs have created the ultimate in casual elegance The Rumi Collection.  Each hand knotted piece is created using a palette of vibrant yarns, which are shorn closely to expose the warp and weft of the rug.  These bold designs are then washed to give the distressed,  vintage look of an heirloom that has been handed down for generations.Please note: Because of the rug's construction and its closely-shorn pile, you will be able to see the warp and weft fibers.  Where weft fibers are tied on to one another, you will notice a slight irregularity in the foundation of the rug.  Please note that this is simply a characteristic of the type of rug, and it is not considered a defect.
construction: Hand knotted in India in an antique washed and closely shorn wool pile.

name: Feizy Burke Rug in Atlantic
meta_title: Feizy Burke Rug in Atlantic
description: The Burke Collection's unique look comes from a technique that combines hand looming and hand knotting.  The result is a collection that has a distressed look but still feels luxurious.  Color varies in intensity throughout the hand spun viscose yarns and the subtle sheen plays beautifully against the more rustic wool fibers.  Thin, flexible and incredibly versatile, these pieces work well in a variety of settings.
construction: Hand loomed and knotted in India in wool and art silk.

description: The Cosmo Collection is a hand tufted bamboo viscose rug hiding a surprise...a jacquard rug on the back!  With completely different, beautifully modern designs on each side in complementary colors, these pieces are versatile, durable and offer the ability to change the look and feel of a room with a simple flip of the rug.
construction: Hand tufted and jacquard backed in India in a bamboo viscose pile.

meta_title: Feizy Sattika Rug in Apricot
